Catalano.Imaging.Filters

Class LevelsLinear

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Imaging.Filters.LevelsLinear
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBaseInPlace

    public class LevelsLinear
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseInPlace
    Linear correction of RGB channels. The filter performs linear correction of RGB channels by mapping specified channels' input ranges to output ranges.
